Feline2::
She looked at HotRod. She took a few steps towards him, looking hjim 
over. He was reminding her of her her past. She looked down, trying 
to reconstruct the images of her self destruction in her mind, but it 
just wasn't there.  Looking at HotRod, she reached out with her hand 
and lightly touched his cheek. She was was trying to remember what he 
had been to her. But she just couldn't find the memories in her 
program.
